author: PostmodernJukebox
description:
“I Swear” by All-4-One Western Swing style cover by Postmodern Jukebox ft. Eva Mikhailovna & Demi Remick.
Get The Song: http://pmjlive.com/iswear | Subscribe: http://bit.ly/subPMJ
World Tour Tix: http://pmjtour.com | PMJ on Spotify: http://pmjlive.com/pmjspotify 

The enchanting Eva Mikhailova returns with another love letter to Old Souls everywhere — this time, we’re taking the All-4-One / John Michael Montgomery ‘90s hit, “I Swear” back to the days of Bob Wills and other Western Swing greats, with some help from PMJ tap dance rhythm wrangler, Demi Remick.
